snippet.title: Panchayat Season 4 - Official Teaser | Jitendra Kumar, Neena Gupta, Raghubir Yadav | Prime Video IN
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Panchayat Season 4 Official Teaser
Starring Jitendra Kumar, Neena Gupta, Raghubir Yadav, Faisal Malik, Chandan Roy, Sanvikaa
Created by Deepak Kumar Mishra, Chandan Kumar
Directed by Akshat Vijaywargiya, Deepak Kumar Mishra
Written by Chandan Kumar
Executive Producers: Deepak Kumar Mishra, Vijay Koshy, Shreyansh Pandey
A TVF Creation

Official Release Date July 2, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Amid intense village panchayat elections, Pradhan and Bhushan’s camps battle through sharp political moves. As Abhishek sheds his neutrality, both his future and Pradhan’s hang in the balance.

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages – including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal – The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video’s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures – Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

#PanchayatOnPrime #panchayatseason4 #teaser #phulera #series #webseries #webseriesonprime #tvf #primevideoindia

es-US.title: Duelo PvP de $100,000 de Dream vs. Daquavis
es-US.description:
Dream vs. Daquavis: Duelo JcJ de $100,000. Este es el desafío JcJ, el primero de nuestro duelo. A continuación, el desafío de las 10 habilidades. ¿Quién ganará?

Sígueme en mis redes sociales:
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic

Daquavis: @DaquavisMC

Estoy empezando mi arco de entrenamiento, y este es el principio. Gracias a todos los que me ayudaron a entrenar la semana pasada para este duelo. Se necesita mucho más entrenamiento para vencer a 6 cazadores. Por ahora, mi principal objetivo es vencer a Daquavis.

hi.title: ड्रीम बनाम डेक्वीस $100,000 PvP द्वंद्वयुद्ध
hi.description:
ड्रीम बनाम डेक्वाविस $100,000 PvP द्वंद्वयुद्ध। यह PvP चुनौती है, हमारे द्वंद्वयुद्ध में पहली चुनौती। अगला 10 कौशल चुनौती है। कौन जीतेगा?

मेरे सोशल मीडिया को फॉलो करें:
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic

डेक्वाविस: @DaquavisMC

मैं अभी अपना प्रशिक्षण आर्क शुरू कर रहा हूँ, और यह इसकी शुरुआत है। पिछले हफ़्ते इस द्वंद्वयुद्ध के लिए मुझे प्रशिक्षित करने में मदद करने वाले सभी लोगों का धन्यवाद। 6 शिकारियों को हराने के लिए बहुत अधिक प्रशिक्षण की आवश्यकता है। अभी के लिए, डेक्वाविस को हराना मेरा मुख्य लक्ष्य है।

fr-FR.title: Duel JcJ Dream VS Daquavis à 100 000 $
fr-FR.description:
Duel JcJ Dream contre Daquavis à 100 000 $. Voici le défi JcJ, le premier de notre duel. Vient ensuite le défi des 10 compétences. Qui va gagner ?

Suivez-moi sur les réseaux sociaux :
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic

Daquavis : @DaquavisMC

Je viens de commencer mon entraînement, et c'est le début. Merci à tous ceux qui m'ont aidé à m'entraîner la semaine dernière pour ce duel. Il me reste encore beaucoup d'entraînement pour vaincre 6 chasseurs. Pour l'instant, vaincre Daquavis est mon objectif principal.

id.title: Duel PvP Dream VS Daquavis senilai $100.000
id.description:
Dream VS Daquavis Duel PvP senilai $100.000. Ini adalah tantangan PvP, tantangan pertama dalam duel kami. Berikutnya adalah tantangan 10 keterampilan. Siapa yang akan menang?

Ikuti media sosial saya:
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic

Daquavis: @DaquavisMC

Saya baru saja memulai perjalanan pelatihan saya, dan ini adalah awalnya. Terima kasih kepada semua orang yang telah membantu saya berlatih minggu lalu untuk duel ini. Masih banyak latihan yang diperlukan untuk mengalahkan 6 pemburu. Untuk saat ini, mengalahkan Daquavis adalah fokus utama saya.

it.title: Duello PvP Dream VS Daquavis da $ 100.000
it.description:
Duello PvP Dream VS Daquavis da 100.000 $. Questa è la sfida PvP, la prima sfida del nostro duello. La prossima è la sfida delle 10 abilità. Chi vincerà?

Seguimi sui social:
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic

Daquavis: @DaquavisMC

Ho appena iniziato il mio arco di addestramento, e questo è solo l'inizio. Grazie a tutti coloro che mi hanno aiutato ad allenarmi la scorsa settimana per questo duello. Ci vorrà molto più allenamento per sconfiggere 6 cacciatori. Per ora, sconfiggere Daquavis è il mio obiettivo principale.

de-DE.title: Dream VS Daquavis $100.000 PvP-Duell
de-DE.description:
Dream VS Daquavis: 100.000 $ PvP-Duell. Dies ist die PvP-Herausforderung, die erste Herausforderung unseres Duells. Als Nächstes folgt die 10-Fähigkeiten-Herausforderung. Wer wird gewinnen?

Folgt mir auf meinen Social-Media-Kanälen:
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic

Daquavis: @DaquavisMC

Ich beginne gerade mit meinem Training, und das ist erst der Anfang. Vielen Dank an alle, die mich letzte Woche beim Training für dieses Duell unterstützt haben. Um sechs Jäger zu besiegen, ist noch viel Training nötig. Im Moment konzentriere ich mich vor allem darauf, Daquavis zu besiegen.

pt-BR.title: Duelo PvP Dream VS Daquavis de US$ 100.000
pt-BR.description:
Duelo PvP Dream VS Daquavis de US$ 100.000. Este é o desafio PvP, o primeiro desafio do nosso duelo. O próximo é o desafio das 10 habilidades. Quem vencerá?

Siga minhas redes sociais:
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic

Daquavis: @DaquavisMC

Estou apenas começando meu ciclo de treinamento, e este é o começo dele. Obrigado a todos que me ajudaram a treinar na semana passada para este duelo. Muito mais treinamento é necessário para derrotar 6 caçadores. Por enquanto, derrotar Daquavis é meu foco principal.

ja.title: ドリーム VS ダクアヴィス $100,000 PvP デュエル
ja.description:
Dream VS Daquavis 10万ドルPvPデュエル。これはPvPチャレンジ、デュエルの最初のチャレンジです。次は10スキルチャレンジです。勝つのは誰でしょうか？

私のソーシャルメディアをフォローしてください：
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic

Daquavis: @DaquavisMC

トレーニングを始めたばかりで、これはまだ序の口です。このデュエルに向けて先週トレーニングを手伝ってくれた皆さんに感謝します。6人のハンターを倒すには、まだまだトレーニングが必要です。今はDaquavisを倒すことが最優先です。

snippet.description:
WB Madhyamik Result 2025: মাধ্যমিক পরীক্ষার পরে মৃত্যু থৈবি মুখোপাধ্যায়ের। লিভারের অসুখ নিয়েই একের পর এক পরীক্ষা।

snippet.title: क्यों हुई Jetha और Iyer के बीच Ugly Fight? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | 1 May 2025
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Popatlal is worried about the huge bill payments. Soon Jethalal and Mr Iyer get into an ugly fight. Everyone in the society asks them to break it off or else, they won't be in talking terms with both of them. Later, Madhavi informs Daya about the fight.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 543
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

list=PLfyXOEyr93G3QQIKGExbP8b1NqpJKa_xb

snippet.title: Shivaji Nu Halardu | Aditya Gadhvi | A Tribute to Shivaji Maharaj |Gujarat & Maharashtra Day Special
snippet.description:
Celebrating Gujarat Day and Maharashtra Day with 'Shivaji Nu Halardu,' a song that salutes the courage and leadership of Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj. With Jhaverchand Meghani’s impactful storytelling and Aditya Gadhvi’s stirring voice, it brings the legendary spirit to life.

આજે ‘ગુજરાત દિવસ’ અને ‘મહારાષ્ટ્ર દિવસ’ ની ઉજવણી વેળાએ રાષ્ટ્રીય શાયર અને લોકસાહિત્યકાર શ્રી ઝવેરચંદ મેઘાણીરચિત શૌર્યરસથી છલકતી અમર રચના ‘શિવાજીનું હાલરડું’ આદિત્ય ગઢવીના પ્રભાવશાળી કંઠે સાંભળીએ.
માતા જીજાબાઈએ પુત્ર શિવાજીને સંભળાવેલું, નીડર થવાનો સંદેશ આપતું આ હાલરડું વીરરસથી છલકે છે, જેમાં બાળ શિવાજીને શૂરવીર બનવાના આશિષની સાથે સાથે મૃત્યુસમાન કષ્ટોનો સામનો કરી, પોતાના જીવનનું બલિદાન આપીને પણ સ્વરાજ મેળવવા માટે માતા મક્કમતાથી આહ્વાન કરે છે.

snippet.title: Annies Kitchen Season 3 | Episode :103 | Malabar Meets Kottayam | Abida Rasheed | Amrita TV
snippet.description:
When Malabar spices meet Kottayam flavors! 🌶️🐟

In today’s flavorful episode of Annie’s Kitchen, we’re in for a spicy surprise as the queen of Malabari cuisine, Chef Abida Rasheed, joins Annie in the kitchen! 🌶️👩‍🍳

Known for her signature touch in traditional Malabar dishes, Abida surprises Annie with a mouth-watering prawns recipe straight from her culinary treasure chest. In return, Annie whips up a delicious Kottayam-style Meen Curry, bringing together the best of two culinary worlds! 🐟🍛

From heartwarming stories about her easygoing parents to her inspiring journey into the world of cooking, Abida shares it all—along with loads of kitchen tips, tricks, and flavor secrets you won’t want to miss!

This episode is a feast of culture, nostalgia, and flavor—don’t miss it! ✨🍽️

"Annie's Kitchen" is a unique and exciting cookery-cum-chat show, airing every Thursday at 9 PM on Amrita TV. In its second season, this delightful program is hosted by the multi-talented and charming Annie Shaji Kailas, a well-known actress in the Indian film industry. Join Annie as she whips up delicious and mouth-watering dishes in the kitchen, showcasing her culinary skills while inviting celebrity guests from the world of entertainment to join her.

                The show is divided into two engaging segments. In the first segment, watch as Annie demonstrates how to prepare a special dish, adding her personal touch and sharing handy cooking tips that will leave you craving more. In the second segment, the real fun begins! Annie sits down for a lively and entertaining chat with her celebrity guests, asking them humorous, intriguing  questions that reveal fascinating stories from their lives and careers.

                                         Annie, who is married to renowned filmmaker Shaji Kailas, brings a perfect blend of warmth and wit to every episode. Together, they have become a beloved couple in the industry, and Annie’s playful charm and insightful interviews make "Annie's Kitchen" a must-watch for viewers of all ages.

Annies Kitchen Let's Cook with Love |Thursday @9 PM |Amrita TV

snippet.description:

🫵🏽 Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/monkeyxmagic/
🥰 Follow Complete Series : https://tinyurl.com/yv7y6ecr

⭐️ Watch Next Episode - https://youtu.be/LoTl_15q9Ws

*Crossing India for Free ~ Original by Monkey Magic*

I met a stranger at Dal Lake, Kashmir and asked if I could stay at his place for free. 
Ansar Bhai is the sweetest human. Feel free to reach out to him for your Shikara Bookings! 
Phone : +91- 9086219318
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/ansaar_14/
 
*About Crossing India for FREE (K2K)* 🇮🇳
What was the last time you pushed yourself out of your comfort zone? 

This is a super fun reality show series where I have to reach Kanyakumari for Free and if I spend some money on the road then I have to earn that money back by doing random jobs on the road itself. 
30 days to reach Kanyakumari 
30 days of daily videos documenting this journey

🫵🏽 Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/monkeyxmagic/
=============================================================

snippet.title: Battle for the High Seas | Clash of Clans New Season
snippet.description:
Take part in the Battle for the High Seas by adorning new Hero Skins — Samurai King, Kyudo Queen, Grand Monk, Royal Ninja, and Cyclone Prince — and choose your side in this legendary tale! Salty sea winds and even saltier sea monsters are rolling through your Village! Get aboard the High Seas Scenery and bring this ancient battle to life in your base! 


Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

snippet.title: Every Foodie Ever | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys
This video shows all the funny things happens with Every Food Lover . 

Also guys Check out MamaEarth's Lemon Shampoo + Conditioner :
Mamaearth : https://bit.ly/4i3JYQO
(Use our code  PAAYALJ2025 to get a 20% off)
You can also buy them from-
Amazon : https://amzn.to/3QZeO1O
Flipkart : https://bit.ly/4i3K1vY
Nykaa : https://bit.ly/42nYVHI

This Video covers different scenarios like The Chole bhature lovers , crazy food vloggers , foodies who crave kachori sabzi , when we go shopping with mom in jwala heri and chandni chowk , we eat gol gappe , dosa sambhar , idli vada , gol gappe after shopping is hraven , juice lovers for energy , momos , ram laddo is a classic but nobody can escape food poising . friends catching up on weekends in cafes eating italian , asian , Chinese , dimsum , pizza , pasta , sanwhich , dessert tiramisu , people who like to binge watch , people who travel around the world just to eat their fav authentic for croissant to paris , pasta italy , sushi japan , nepali momos nepal , samosa india . true purani dilli food lovers love bedmi puri travel 1 hour just to eat garam garam nagori . 
How Indians behave in cafes and restaurants. The Bhukkads , you know the over eaters who wants to eat everything , diet conscious, judgy people who love to gossip, newly married couple, couples on date , fighting couples, college friends bunking , problematic people who keeps changing the seats , weird waiter , that funny middle class family having their sunday outing.

This video is filled with food  memories and situations we all have been in . 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories of every foodie ever
Do share it with your friends and family , Relatives , Neighbour . .. Comment down your Fav Part , 
Like , Share and 
Subscribe to our Channel - http://bit.ly/thepaayaljain | Press Bell Icon

Follow Us On Instagram

Tena Jaiin : https://www.instagram.com/tenajaiin/?...

Location : Elito Cafe , https://maps.app.goo.gl/N4vsyeDaJaFubTtN6?g_st=iw

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada

snippet.title: How To Achieve Financial Freedom? By Sandeep Maheshwari | Hindi
snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

Uma deliciosa receita típica da aldeia que você não vai querer perder!

de-DE.title: Hähnchenschenkel essen | Gebratene Hähnchenschenkel mit Tomatensauce | Wie man Tomatensauce nach ...

Ein köstliches Rezept nach Dorfart, das Sie nicht verpassen sollten!

id.title: MAKANAN PAHA AYAM | Paha Ayam Goreng Saus Tomat | Cara Membuat Saus Tomat ala Desa

Saksikan bagaimana kami membuat saus tomat yang kaya dan beraroma dari bahan-bahan segar dan menggoreng paha ayam yang empuk dengan sempurna. Resep lezat ala desa yang tidak boleh Anda lewatkan!

hi.title: चिकन लेग्स खाना | टमाटर सॉस के साथ फ्राइड चिकन लेग्स | टमाटर सॉस विलेज स्टाइल कैसे बनाएं
hi.description: पारंपरिक ग्रामीण शैली में तैयार, ताज़ी पकी हुई टमाटर की चटनी के साथ परोसे गए तले हुए चिकन पैरों के कुरकुरे स्वाद का आनंद लें। देखें कि हम कैसे ताज़ी सामग्री से भरपूर, स्वादिष्ट टमाटर की चटनी बनाते हैं और कोमल चिकन पैरों को बेहतरीन तरीके से तलते हैं। एक स्वादिष्ट ग्रामीण शैली की रेसिपी जिसे आप मिस नहीं करना चाहेंगे!

Une délicieuse recette villageoise à ne pas manquer !

ja.title: 鶏もも肉の食べ方｜トマトソースで揚げた鶏もも肉｜村流トマトソースの作り方
ja.description: 伝統的な村のスタイルで調理された、揚げたてのトマトソースを添えた、カリカリのフライドチキンレッグをお楽しみください。新鮮な食材から濃厚で風味豊かなトマトソースを作り、柔らかいチキンレッグを完璧に揚げる様子をご覧ください。絶対に見逃せない、村のスタイルの美味しいレシピです！

it.title: MANGIARE COSCE DI POLLO | Cosce di pollo fritte con salsa di pomodoro | Come preparare la salsa d...

Guardate come prepariamo una salsa di pomodoro ricca e saporita con ingredienti freschi e come friggiamo alla perfezione le tenere cosce di pollo. Una deliziosa ricetta contadina da non perdere!

snippet.title: Ghum Hai Kisikey Pyaar Meiin | Ek Haadse Se Uthe Kayi Sawaal
snippet.description:

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4386 - Gogi Hua Society Se Gayab! | Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Gokuldham Society | Gada Electronics | Bonus | Financial Year

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. Are you ready for the challenge? 

 Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  #GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame


Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Mann Mast Malang Episode 30 Teaser - 27th April 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Mann Mast Malang is a love story that traces the journey of two families who, once close and united by their children's engagement, become sworn enemies due to a single incident. As the story unfolds, Kabeer and Riya, former fiancés turned enemies, start to grow closer and eventually fall in love. Their love story faces the challenge of uniting their feuding families, as they strive to make their love successful against all odds.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Ali Faizan
Writer: Nooran Makhdoom

Cast:
Danish Taimoor as Kabir

snippet.title: My Hair care routine || Niha Sisters || My Hair growth journey ||
snippet.description:
Haircare Routine : Step-by-Step Guide

1. Oil Massage Before Shampooing :
Regular oiling nourishes the scalp, reduces dryness, strengthens hair follicles, and adds shine over time. Always massage your scalp gently to promote better blood circulation.

2. Essential Oil Addition :
Mix 3 drops of essential oil like rosemary with your carrier oil to boost hair growth. Additionally, after every wash, spray rosemary water on your scalp for improved results.

3. Use Mild Shampoos and Conditioners :
Choose mild shampoos instead of harsh, chemical-laden products. Always condition your hair after every wash, especially if you have frizzy hair. Otherwise, condition at least twice a week. Try reverse conditioning (conditioning before shampoo) twice a month for extra nourishment.

4. Weekly Hair Mask Routine :
Apply a mild or homemade hair mask once a week to deeply condition and hydrate your hair. Regular use improves texture, adds shine, and reduces frizz and breakage.

5. Use Lukewarm or Cool Water :
Always rinse your hair with lukewarm or cool water. Hot water strips away natural oils, making hair dry and more prone to breakage.

6. Gentle Shampooing Technique :
Avoid rubbing the scalp harshly. Apply an adequate amount of shampoo and gently massage with your fingertips or a hair massaging tool. When rinsing, carefully squeeze out excess water without twisting or pulling the hair.

7. Scalp Care :
Maintaining a clean, healthy scalp promotes better hair growth. Exfoliate the scalp gently and keep it moisturized. Wash your hair 2–3 times a week.

8. Switch to Microfiber Towels :
Replace regular towels with microfiber towels. They are softer and much gentler on both hair and scalp, reducing friction and breakage.

9. Hair Serum Application : 
Hair serum plays a vital role during the hair growth journey. It locks in moisture and smooths frizz. Always apply serum on damp or towel-dried hair, not dry hair.

10. Avoid Heat Styling Tools :
Minimize or completely avoid heat styling tools like dryers, straighteners, and curlers. If you must use them, always apply a heat protectant spray to shield your hair from damage.

11. Sleep on Satin Pillowcases : 
Sleeping on satin pillowcases reduces friction, prevents frizz, and is much gentler on your hair. If possible, sleep without pillows for better blood circulation, but ensure you are still resting on a satin surface.

12. Cover Your Hair When Going Out :
Shield your hair from dust, pollution, and UV rays by covering it with a scarf, bandana, or using a silk-lined cap under helmets. Alternatively, opt for loose buns or braids instead of leaving your hair open.

13. Tie Hair in a Braid or Loose Bun :
Tying hair in a loose braid or bun helps minimize friction and breakage compared to tighter hairstyles like ponytails.

14. Switch to a Wooden Comb :
Use a wooden comb instead of plastic. Wooden combs help reduce static, distribute natural oils evenly, enhance shine, and are gentler, minimizing hair breakage.

15. Night Haircare Routine :
Before sleeping, gently comb your hair with a wooden comb and secure it in a protective hairstyle (like a loose braid). Sleep on a satin pillowcase for added protection.

16. Focus on Food Intake :
Nutrition is crucial. Consume protein and iron-rich foods like boiled eggs (once or twice a day), green vegetables, and fruits. Monitor your iron levels, as iron deficiency can cause hair fall. Additionally, soak almonds overnight, drink the water, and eat the soaked almonds the next morning for great results.

17. Choose the Right Haircut :
Haircuts play an important role. For volume and bounce, basic U-cuts and straight cuts work well, especially for thinning hair. Avoid layers, feathers, or V-cuts if you’re experiencing hair fall. Regularly trim split ends to support healthy hair growth.

18. Be Cautious with Hair Treatments :
Research thoroughly before opting for any hair treatments. Personally, treatments like keratin caused damage rather than improvements. Stick to natural methods unless absolutely necessary.


---

Important Final Note:

Patience is key. Visible results like baby hairs may take 3–6 months.

Initial hair fall is normal when introducing rosemary, but it should gradually decrease over time.

Monitor your hair: If excessive hair fall persists after 1–1.5 months, reconsider the products you're using, as they might not be suitable for you.
